title: Your main accidentally leaves their computer open, and you see their internet history
body:
Your main accidentally leaves their computer open, and you see their internet history. What do you find?

What's kumiho?
I think the difference is that a Kumiho eats people or something...

A *kumiho* is Korean, and eats human livers (living or recently living, usually)  to extend its/her life. A *kumiho* can become human and redeem itself by refraining from eating said livers for a while, although the exact time varies (I believe 9 years is common).

A *kitsune* is Japanese, and typically a more simple trickster. They can be malicious, but the usual fare is just drinking/eating everything and getting people lost, I believe. Some of them can actually be positive forces, protecting certain areas or people that were nice to them and providing blessings to crops. They can also be horribly destructive if insulted.

Obviously, Ahri wasn't eating livers, but the principle was the same.
